elements.name: Borrowing Calculator validation for verifying Borrowing Capacity and Start Over button

steps.name: I am on the Borrower Calculator Page
I enter application type as Single
I enter number of dependants as 0
I enter property you would like to buy as home to live in
I enter my income before tax as 80000
I enter my other income as 10000
I enter my living expenses as 500
I enter current HomeLoan repayments as 0
I enter other loan repayments as 100
I enter total Credit Card limits as 10000
I click on Work out how much I could borrow button
I validate that correct borrowing capacity $507,000 is displayed
I click on Start over button
I enter my living expenses as 1
I click on Work out how much I could borrow button
I should see the borrowing error text
